Database Schema¶

| column_name   | data_type   |
|:--------------|:------------|
| id            | character   |

| tags          | jsonb       |
| content       | text        |

| column_name   | data_type   |

| seen_at       | bigint      |

| banner             | text        |

| software           | text        |
| version            | text        |
| privacy_policy     | text        |

| limitation         | jsonb       |
